text: Sohag Gazi (born August 5, 1991, Barisal) is a Bangladeshi cricketer. He made his Test debut in first test against West Indies in 2012.Sohag Gazi, Abul Hasan get maiden Bangladesh call-ups, Cricinfo taking six wickets in the second innings. ==Reference== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:People from Barisal Division
